➜陇南诗词：蜀道申遗，青泥流韵
http://www.sohu.com/a/426830477_804243	41967
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201023/b759cb47dc784facb60d9b50813829db.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥流韵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赵芳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（一）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">踏上青泥岭（古风）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">踏上青泥岭，诗词比天高。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">金徽呈大器，谪仙最逍遥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（二）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥流韵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">盘盘吟蜀道，今古两堪题。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飞鸟难成影，狂人敢揭迷。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">锁咽谁折梦，穿甲越青泥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天岭自调色，娇莺恰恰啼。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何革</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥知行客怨，千载苦青泥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">地老猿声古，荆深鸟径迷。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岭云浮陇蜀，崖水跌高低。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李杜吟哦在，我来焉敢题。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201023/6d55710de1a8484f856193c9cf6d073d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭杂咏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（一）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李蔚斌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">昔曾身在铁山阿，才识道穷其奈何。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云表氤氲来即去，涧溪呜咽哭如歌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一丸泥足闻鸡早，百丈关高得月多。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是圣是仙空自在，吟留终不忆秦娥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（二）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李蔚斌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绝顶尤藏十万阿，散关长琐月如何。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">临川罔顾秦川咏，借道盲从蜀道歌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">趁早黄鹂声自远，栖迟白鹭影涵多。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长生藉此凌霄殿，曷必无端问素娥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（三）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李蔚斌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">离离草又结深阿，西岭逶迤道几何。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">漫卷诗书柳羌笛，新摇云水洞仙歌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坦途除却穷途少，胜景全凭异景多。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更得春风长此住，陇梅重点出青娥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201023/a3aebeac87674002aae40b0dffddb88d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">张泓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">太白高吟蜀道难，诗坛从此降谪仙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">千秋一座青泥岭，赢得声名压陕川。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">咏青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文川</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">盘盘折折青泥岭，李白曾嗟蜀道难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天堑通途惊巨变，常教骚客醉其间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼树雄</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">未到青泥总说难，而今蜀道任游观。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">扶摇直上三千尺，纵横飞旋百二盘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">驿外流连聆古迹，碑旁怀谒慰金銮。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">情思最爱吟工部，不尽长河滚滚叹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201023/4a0d0bdfbcd349deabe88a8dfa53e5df.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦萦青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">张庆中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人道青泥岭，奇峰敢摸天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青莲留醉呓，子美记行躔。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">路险猿难越，林幽鸟不迁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">申遗当有据，聚会陕甘川。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秦波</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李杜吟叹蜀道难，青泥峻岭耸云巅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今朝申遗承文运，圆梦千年敬谪仙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">【菩萨蛮】</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问道青泥岭（新韵）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋雨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秦音蜀道青泥岭，雄鸡一唱闻三省。幽径草丛生，罕听车马声。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">史垂千古韵，墨客何惜吝。古驿复无期，风光今胜昔。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201023/1ebdaa6ae6d1418687e0c67f2b20be96.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">庚子季秋登青泥岭有寄</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">廖正荣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">望里丹青画最工，层林艳丽着黄红。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">欲教蜀道山光秀，好让青泥气象雄。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">修竹几行常翠翠，飞鸿一字太匆匆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">细听溪涧潺潺水，合是蒙童诵国风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">己亥六月十二与陇南诗词师友登青泥岭随感</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">张巧红</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">走进金徽抬眼观，青泥如铁入云端。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杜甫嗟讶崖倾径，李白狂呼蜀道难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">新路逶迤通岭上，巅峰耸立阻飞鸾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">巉岩珍木随溪见，始晓诗篇不妄叹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">【天门谣】</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赵书成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">层峻青泥岭。极雄伟、古今幽境。诗圣咏。谪仙留豪兴。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陇阻蜀关人文隽永。信史长存增后劲。添富盛。逐个数、传承驰竞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201023/c6b0337335fa4d11be3d3d53037410dc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">屈学文</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥高险峻，自古路盘盘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李杜曾嗟叹，而今栈道宽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭（新韵）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">马娃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不惧岩峦近九重，驱车故道览遗踪。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当年铁岭何其幸，却与诗流万古名。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蜀道青泥（新韵）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">田雨燕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">太白惊惧叹盘盘，千载流传蜀道难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高速轻车观翠岭，诗仙重访作何篇？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201023/3c80d341a6a4401eb013fe41ed6daf38.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">徽州不缺席（古风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">张国栋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥申世遗，蜀道居正席。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">铁山鸟无踪，狂人当李白。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">登青泥岭感怀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">张敬年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">览尽风光攀越岭，丹青绝壁露峥嵘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">金徽美酒甲天下，更有诗仙醉卧名。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">注：曾有李白醉卧青泥岭之说。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青岭古道吟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何郑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥蜀道悬崖峙，古栈金徽走圣贤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再阅赋篇叹险岭，又彰狭隘弹新弦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云横雨湿三霄凤，径难峰盘九重天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陇上江南丰裕地，申遗定胜喜空前。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201023/df9dcf47a512438e8eef25b8b8731504.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭申遗感怀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（新韵）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高永久</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蜀道青泥岭，崎岖尽险关，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双峰多壮景，五柳有名篇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">眼望千秋月，诗吟万仞山。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">申遗扬世界，怀古话桑田。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陈永红</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李杜传诗犹梦幻，青泥岭险路盘盘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云霞万里追仙圣，百折千回蜀道难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭(新韵)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朱俊强</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">磅礴气势傲蓝天，横卧云端不见巅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">徒步青泥几倒绕，举足石径数盘旋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">玄宗过岭飞波涌，李杜挥诗叹道难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">九域英雄皆敬畏，金戈铁马闯奇关。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201023/92d4cfd568f34eaab2d6b74fac679fd5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">张羽中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭上话神奇，李白逍遥杜甫词。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">道尽明皇风与月，吴家兄弟展雄姿。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥古道吟（新韵）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">王会军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥巍峨染秋光，蜀道逶迤汉水长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丞相辕门挥斧钺，吴阶帐外射天狼。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重来古驿寻工部，又到成州饮杜康。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">且看今朝千里景，江山处处有新章。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">张桂琴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百步九盘青泥岭，猿猱昔日畏攀缘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">申遗圆了诗仙梦，醉酒重吟蜀道篇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭（新韵）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨月忠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蜀道青泥岭，盘盘入九天。诗吟千古句，笔状万崇山。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">石栈惊霄路，洪波转逆川。申遗留史册，美酒慰谪仙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201023/4c52faef969c4899bde5355661ad7ad3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">姜毓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">悬崖深万仞，泥岭入云端。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">峰叠盘途险，方知蜀道难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赵云</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陇秦要塞耸云巅，历史人文各斐然。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绝顶览观长记梦，唤来李杜驻诗贤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蜀道青泥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">王得虎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥上云天十八盘，青泥蜀道越千年。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谪仙醉笔书清韵，狂世豪篇压众贤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201023/15f9a725251141519c8bf4d78a8703ff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋吟青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何巧巧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">盘盘飘玉带，峰顶雾云缭。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">欢喜摩天岭，层峦雨后娆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋风妆两树，疑似客行潇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">盘点青泥赋，钦嗟李杜描。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭（新韵）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">申贵怀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">崇山峻岭入云端，揽胜吟诗仰圣贤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雾锁青泥寻古道，愧无佳句记流年。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">【采桑子】</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">咏青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨月忠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蜀秦要道青泥岭，万仞垂悬，沟泄飞湍，鸟道羊肠入九天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谪仙豪气留青史，揽胜追贤。盛世承传。文运千秋甘陕川。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201023/8d846dd2e2534cdebfb2a659f6376f95.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭（古风）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李明</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蜀道盘盘困谪仙，千年绝壁鬼门关。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如今高速穿山过，陇上江南慰圣贤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭（古风）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛勇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">徽州青泥岭盘盘。太白曾叹蜀道难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而今金徽誉天下，高速客流景含烟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赵晓滨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">忆昔骚人过铁山，青泥巉险失声颜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">魂惊蜀道谪仙赋，乱避秦川诗圣艰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大路而今通峻岭，乡翁犹自走溪湾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">四时千壑风光异，墨客寻幽醉此间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201023/b3bb3c88fa3f479bae03cd2dc2f4d2d6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭四叹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">郭军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一条蜀道五千峦，半壁青泥九十盘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">东界山遥云海隐，虞关未过又三滩。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仙人关险思吴玠，神鬼临门不向东。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无计更怜金兀术，英雄狭路遇英雄。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一山未过千山出，抬眼云来脚下惊。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李白青泥行路叹，嘉陵江渺变涛声。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">醉卧青泥岭上岚，敢邀李白把诗谈。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尔来不过金徽酒，常叫骚人赞陇南。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">【惜琼花】</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">登嘉陵鸡关山隘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">郭军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">嘉陵碧，春树密。望鸡关隘路，风静云白。忽焉身在三滩北。怀古凭栏，边角沉戟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宋疆图，金国檄。大明征战鼓，弹指朝夕。故山人隐青泥寂。今友来兮，歌酒情溢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201023/d8d8425d34054b45968b59756fe21838.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蜀道青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何水长</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">魏巍盘曲黑泥岗，太白嗟乎蜀道殇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">汹涌波涛惊巨蟒，通途古隘换新航。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">张寒喜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥故道霸王鞭，奇险幽深荡碧烟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也有文人描峻岭，曾经武将画金川。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诗仙举目生佳句，杜甫低眉出妙联。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自古春苗繁翳茂，而今秋草亮郊廛。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭（古风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">张卫红</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大美河池千古韵，青泥岭径九龙盘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谪仙醉卧铭章问，诗圣西霞隽墨翰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三两飞鸾松鹤歇，万般景色染层峦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云烟深处通桥栈，骚客惊叹蜀道难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201023/3b57b54d67764e57bcb4472ccb5f7585.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭之险崖栈道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赵文强</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">兀兀青泥岭，悠悠古道连。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">峰回途绕绕，崖险栈绵绵。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">申遗千秋计，恩荫万代传。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">各方同进谏，入世慰先贤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朱艳秀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李杜率先攀，皆言蜀道难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">笔峰连险境，诗路有奇观。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看雾寻云海，携尘傍水滩。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">林深何及尽，上下复盘盘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 【如梦令】</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥古秘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李广娟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">常探青泥古秘，沉醉盛唐文记。远道叹诗仙，蜀道路行天际。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">奇迹，奇迹，千古文章追媲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201023/b83bd652ee554dd4accb96d07d7003f3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">董少文</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">巍峻铁山岭，连绵上九盘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朝烟迷故塞，暮雨阻泥丸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">越堑青莲咏，望乡工部叹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">通途穿险豁，蜀道不愁难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">徽县青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">王建花</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">依陇入蜀天，百步断云烟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">子美嗟乎久，青莲绕道难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飞桥疑断路，沟壑胆边寒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今驾轻车去，遥遥一梦间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蜀道青泥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">康益</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蜀道难。古道难。难煞先人数百年。诗仙感咏叹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岭盘盘。步盘盘。步入青泥思圣贤。现今更好看。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201023/825b7107e0714a70a7597fc677adddd6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陈新峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蜀道雄关险象环，青泥岭上景斑斓。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">武皇疗疾传佳话，李杜当年吓变颜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">约聚青泥岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">郑军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">龙盘曲径入云端，天堑通途蜀道难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雅士青泥研李杜，兴游祝酒上诗坛。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阴平古道青泥岭（古风)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">侯世山</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雄关漫道青泥岭，入蜀难于上青天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">众志城城不惧险，宏图展志出雄贤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阴平古道多佳话，茶马流韵数千年。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">兵家相争黄金地，如今申遗史册传。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201023/dae0b0ada307418eb9d8d5b33167d1e9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来源：陇南诗词</p>
